    <entry>
      <title>github_hexo博客创建</title>
      <link href="/2022/05/10/github_hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA/"/>
      <url>/2022/05/10/github_hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="GitHub博客创建"><a href="#GitHub博客创建" class="headerlink" title="GitHub博客创建"></a>GitHub博客创建</h1><h2 id="一、需要安装的软件"><a href="#一、需要安装的软件" class="headerlink" title="一、需要安装的软件"></a>一、需要安装的软件</h2><h3 id="1、Node-js下载"><a href="#1、Node-js下载" class="headerlink" title="1、Node.js下载"></a>1、Node.js下载</h3><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v4.2.3/node-v4.2.3-x64.msi%EF%BC%88%E6%95%99%E5%AD%A6%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%EF%BC%89">https://nodejs.org/dist/v4.2.3/node-v4.2.3-x64.msi（教学版本）</a></p><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%EF%BC%89">https://nodejs.org/en/download/（最新版本）</a></p><p>【它让JavaScript成为与PHP、Python、Perl、Ruby等服务端语言平起平坐的脚本语言。】</p><p>安装教程：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/liuqiyun/p/8133904.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/liuqiyun/p/8133904.html</a></p><p>其他的nodejs教程：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/huanhao/p/hexobase.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/huanhao/p/hexobase.html</a></p><h3 id="2、Git下载"><a href="#2、Git下载" class="headerlink" title="2、Git下载"></a>2、Git下载</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/git-for-windows/git/releases/download/v2.11.0.windows.3/Git-2.11.0.3-64-bit.exe">https://github.com/git-for-windows/git/releases/download/v2.11.0.windows.3/Git-2.11.0.3-64-bit.exe</a></p><p>【Git是一个开源的分布式版本控制系统，可以有效、高速地处理从很小到非常大的项目版本管理】</p><p>安装教程：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/xueweisuoyong/p/11914045.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/xueweisuoyong/p/11914045.html</a></p><h2 id="二、后续操作"><a href="#二、后续操作" class="headerlink" title="二、后续操作"></a>二、后续操作</h2><h3 id="1、在cmd端"><a href="#1、在cmd端" class="headerlink" title="1、在cmd端"></a>1、在cmd端</h3><p>win+R，输入cmd进入cmd端口</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v <span class="comment">#检查nodejs版本</span></span><br><span class="line">npm -v <span class="comment">#检查npm版本</span></span><br><span class="line">git --version <span class="comment">#检查git版本</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g <span class="comment">#Hexo下载</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo -v <span class="comment">#检查hexo版本</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在cmd端口跳转到指定文件夹位置</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /d file_place</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、拥有一个github账号"><a href="#2、拥有一个github账号" class="headerlink" title="2、拥有一个github账号"></a>2、拥有一个github账号</h3><p>github账号注册：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv5107169/">https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv5107169/</a></p><h3 id="3、在Git-Bath端"><a href="#3、在Git-Bath端" class="headerlink" title="3、在Git Bath端"></a>3、在Git Bath端</h3><h4 id="（1）打开Git-Bath"><a href="#（1）打开Git-Bath" class="headerlink" title="（1）打开Git Bath"></a>（1）打开Git Bath</h4><p>方法一：在cmd端口打开Git Bath：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">start <span class="string">&quot;Open Git Bash&quot;</span> <span class="string">&quot;%SYSTEMDRIVE%\Program Files\Git\git-bash.exe&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>方法二：对目标文件夹用鼠标右键点击，选择“Git Bath Here”</p><h4 id="（2）在Git-Bath端输入"><a href="#（2）在Git-Bath端输入" class="headerlink" title="（2）在Git Bath端输入"></a>（2）在Git Bath端输入</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">&quot;邮箱地址&quot;</span>   <span class="comment">#生成ssh</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com      <span class="comment">#测试ssh是否绑定成功</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo init <span class="comment">#初始化hexo博客</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s <span class="comment">#启动服务</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装hexo-deployer-git自动部署发布工具：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h6 id><a href="#" class="headerlink" title></a></h6><h4 id="（3）修改博客根目录文件"><a href="#（3）修改博客根目录文件" class="headerlink" title="（3）修改博客根目录文件"></a>（3）修改博客根目录文件</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">根目录的D:\Blog\GitHubBlog\_config.yml：</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https://github.com/TreeioView/TreeioView.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="（4）在Git-Bath端输入"><a href="#（4）在Git-Bath端输入" class="headerlink" title="（4）在Git Bath端输入"></a>（4）在Git Bath端输入</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g <span class="comment">#生成</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d<span class="comment">#本地文件上传到GitHub仓库</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h6 id="资料来源于：【2021最新版】保姆级Hexo-github搭建个人博客-哔哩哔哩-bilibili"><a href="#资料来源于：【2021最新版】保姆级Hexo-github搭建个人博客-哔哩哔哩-bilibili" class="headerlink" title="资料来源于：【2021最新版】保姆级Hexo+github搭建个人博客_哔哩哔哩_bilibili"></a>资料来源于：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1mU4y1j72n?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0">【2021最新版】保姆级Hexo+github搭建个人博客_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></h6><h4 id="（5）Hexo指令"><a href="#（5）Hexo指令" class="headerlink" title="（5）Hexo指令"></a>（5）Hexo指令</h4><p><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands.html">指令 | Hexo</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
