        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="PPET：桌面看板娘"><a href="#PPET：桌面看板娘" class="headerlink" title="PPET：桌面看板娘"></a>PPET：桌面看板娘</h1><h2 id="一、项目地址"><a href="#一、项目地址" class="headerlink" title="一、项目地址"></a>一、项目地址</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/zenghongtu/PPet">zenghongtu&#x2F;PPet: 👻在你的桌面放一个萌妹子，多一点乐趣😏~（支持Mac、Win和Linux） (github.com)</a></p><p>新版本：v3.3.0</p><p>下载地址：<a href="https://github.com/zenghongtu/PPet/releases/download/v3.3.0/PPet3_3.3.0.exe">https://github.com/zenghongtu/PPet/releases/download/v3.3.0/PPet3_3.3.0.exe</a></p><p>旧版本：1.2.1</p><p>下载地址：<a href="https://github.com/zenghongtu/PPet/releases/download/v1.2.1/PPet-1.2.1.exe">https://github.com/zenghongtu/PPet/releases/download/v1.2.1/PPet-1.2.1.exe</a></p><h2 id="二、模型使用"><a href="#二、模型使用" class="headerlink" title="二、模型使用"></a>二、模型使用</h2><h3 id="1-初始Model"><a href="#1-初始Model" class="headerlink" title="1.初始Model"></a>1.初始Model</h3><p>刚下载完，应用只有22娘的模型</p><p><img src="https://github.com/zenghongtu/PPet/raw/dev/assets/record1.gif" alt="img"></p><h3 id="2-引用线上Model"><a href="#2-引用线上Model" class="headerlink" title="2.引用线上Model"></a>2.引用线上Model</h3><p>复制 <a href="https://github.com/zenghongtu/live2d-model-assets/blob/master/assets/model.index">https://github.com/zenghongtu/live2d-model-assets/blob/master/assets/model.index</a> 中的内容，填入 PPet 模型列表中。</p><h3 id="3-引用本地Model"><a href="#3-引用本地Model" class="headerlink" title="3.引用本地Model"></a>3.引用本地Model</h3><h4 id="（1）线上可下载的Model资源"><a href="#（1）线上可下载的Model资源" class="headerlink" title="（1）线上可下载的Model资源"></a>（1）线上可下载的Model资源</h4><table><thead><tr><th>names</th><th>url</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/zenghongtu/live2d-model-assets">zenghongtu&#x2F;live2d-model-assets (github.com)</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/xiazeyu/live2d-widget-models">xiazeyu&#x2F;live2d-widget-models: The model library for live2d-widget.js</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/summerscar/live2dDemo">summerscar&#x2F;live2dDemo: live2dDemo http://summerscar.me/live2dDemo/</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/alg-wiki/AzurLaneL2DViewer">alg-wiki&#x2F;AzurLaneL2DViewer</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/Eikanya/Live2d-model">Eikanya&#x2F;Live2d-model: Live2d model collection</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/xiaoski/live2d_models_collection">xiaoski&#x2F;live2d_models_collection: Collections of live2d models</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/iCharlesZ/vscode-live2d-models">iCharlesZ&#x2F;vscode-live2d-models: VSCode看板娘模型库</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/luanshizhimei/live2d_models_collect">luanshizhimei&#x2F;live2d_models_collect: 个人收集的Live2D模型</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/jianchengwang/live2d_models">jianchengwang&#x2F;live2d_models: 萌萌哒的看板娘</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://mx.paul.ren/">梦象 (paul.ren)</a></td></tr></tbody></table><h4 id="（2）本地Model的引用"><a href="#（2）本地Model的引用" class="headerlink" title="（2）本地Model的引用"></a>（2）本地Model的引用</h4><h5 id="1）导入的方法："><a href="#1）导入的方法：" class="headerlink" title="1）导入的方法："></a>1）导入的方法：</h5><p>引用的本地路径前加 <code>file://</code> ，举例：</p><p><code>file://D:/ppet/live2d_models/un1_2model/live2d/model/nep/model.json</code></p><p>但是Windows系统的间隔符是反斜杠“\”，举例</p><p><code>D:\ppet\live2d_models\un1_2model\live2d\model\nep\model.json</code></p><p>将含有本地模型的文件夹拖入看板娘显示窗口中，导入成功会更新到模型列表中。直接拖拽自动产生的引用路径是反斜杠“\”，PPET无法识别，会导致模型无法显示。</p><p>现写一个python脚本，自动把反斜杠“\”改成斜杠“&#x2F;”。</p><p>modify_character.py</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pyperclip</span><br><span class="line">char = pyperclip.paste()</span><br><span class="line">char = <span class="built_in">list</span>(char)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(char)):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> char[x] == <span class="string">&#x27;\\&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">char[x] = <span class="string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">char = <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>.join(char)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#char = &#x27;file://&#x27;+char</span></span><br><span class="line">pyperclip.copy(char)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#print(&quot;succeed!&quot;)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="2）脚本的使用方法是："><a href="#2）脚本的使用方法是：" class="headerlink" title="2）脚本的使用方法是："></a>2）脚本的使用方法是：</h5><p>1.将含有本地模型的文件夹拖入看板娘显示窗口中；</p><p>2.打开配置的 PPet 模型列表，ctrl + X，剪切全部地址；</p><p>3.运行脚本程序；</p><p>4.再进入配置的 PPet 模型列表，ctrl + V。</p><p>以<code>file://D:\ppet\live2d_models\un1_2modeyel\live2d\model\nep\model.json</code>为例，</p><p>运行结果为：<code>file://D:/ppet/live2d_models/un1_2model/live2d/model/nep/model.json</code></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
