        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo-Blog主题美化"><a href="#Hexo-Blog主题美化" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Blog主题美化"></a>Hexo Blog主题美化</h1><h2 id="一、其他人的优秀博客"><a href="#一、其他人的优秀博客" class="headerlink" title="一、其他人的优秀博客"></a>一、其他人的优秀博客</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Blog introducion</th><th>Blog URL</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>个人博客网址</td><td><a href="https://treeioview.github.io/">treeioview (treeioview.github.io)</a></td></tr><tr><td>Butterfly Chocolate版</td><td><a href="https://yangchaoyi.vip/">https://yangchaoyi.vip</a></td></tr><tr><td>Naccl.Blog</td><td><a href="https://naccl.top/home">https://naccl.top/home</a></td></tr><tr><td>aurora主题</td><td><a href="https://aurora.xcye.xyz/readme/">https://aurora.xcye.xyz/readme/</a></td></tr><tr><td>小游网</td><td><a href="https://xiaoyou66.com/">https://xiaoyou66.com/</a></td></tr><tr><td>itsNeko主题</td><td><a href="https://dyfa.top/page/2/">https://dyfa.top/page/2/</a></td></tr><tr><td>火车啦啦</td><td><a href="https://ihcll.cn/">https://ihcll.cn/</a></td></tr><tr><td>Alan</td><td><a href="https://www.alanwang.site/">https://www.alanwang.site/</a></td></tr><tr><td>Matery  LuckySec版</td><td><a href="http://luckyzmj.cn/">http://luckyzmj.cn/</a></td></tr><tr><td>千羽</td><td><a href="https://nateshao.gitee.io/">https://nateshao.gitee.io</a></td></tr><tr><td>Yuumiy</td><td><a href="https://yuumiy.github.io/">https://yuumiy.github.io/</a></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="二、可使用博客开源代码"><a href="#二、可使用博客开源代码" class="headerlink" title="二、可使用博客开源代码"></a>二、可使用博客开源代码</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Web introducion</th><th>Web URL</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Naccl&#x2F;NBlog</td><td><a href="https://github.com/Naccl/NBlog">Naccl&#x2F;NBlog: 🍓 Spring Boot + Vue 前后端分离博客系统 https://naccl.top (github.com)</a></td></tr><tr><td>LuckyZmj&#x2F;LuckyBlog</td><td><a href="https://github.com/LuckyZmj/LuckyBlog">LuckyZmj&#x2F;LuckyBlog: 基于Hexo+Matery的LuckyBlog开源博客搭建教程，演示站点：www.luckyzmj.cn (github.com)</a></td></tr><tr><td>Chocolate1999&#x2F;hexo-blog-lionkk</td><td><a href="https://github.com/Chocolate1999/hexo-blog-lionkk">Chocolate1999&#x2F;hexo-blog-lionkk: 魔改自butterfly 主题，提供完整详细的文档，同时为了回馈开源，这不是生成后的网页文件，是您可以直接使用的源码，您只需要把博客相关信息换成您自己的就可以部署了，对于新手或者不懂编程的小伙伴来说，简直是福音！ (github.com)</a></td></tr><tr><td>小游网博客开源</td><td><a href="https://xiaoyou66.com/archives/2696">小游网博客开源 (xiaoyou66.com)</a><br><a href="https://github.com/xiaoyou-bilibili/xblog">xiaoyou-bilibili&#x2F;xblog: xblog博客系统 (github.com)</a></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="三、各大主题官网使用教程"><a href="#三、各大主题官网使用教程" class="headerlink" title="三、各大主题官网使用教程"></a>三、各大主题官网使用教程</h2><table><thead><tr><th>主题</th><th>主题官网网址</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Aurora</td><td><a href="https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/guide/getting-started.html#what-is-next">https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/guide/getting-started.html#what-is-next</a></td></tr><tr><td>Yun</td><td><a href="https://yun.yunyoujun.cn/guide/#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B">使用指南 | Hexo-Theme-Yun (yunyoujun.cn)</a></td></tr><tr><td>Matery</td><td><a href="https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery">blinkfox&#x2F;hexo-theme-matery： 一个美丽的hexo博客主题，具有材料设计和响应式设计而成。一个基于材料设计和响应式设计而成的全面、美观的Hexo主题。国内访问：http://blinkfox.com (github.com)</a></td></tr><tr><td>Butterfly</td><td><a href="https://butterfly.js.org/">Butterfly - A Simple and Card UI Design theme for Hexo</a></td></tr><tr><td>3-hexo</td><td><a href="https://github.com/yelog/hexo-theme-3-hexo">https://github.com/yelog/hexo-theme-3-hexo</a></td></tr><tr><td>Next</td><td><a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next</a></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="四、更换新主题的主流程"><a href="#四、更换新主题的主流程" class="headerlink" title="四、更换新主题的主流程"></a>四、更换新主题的主流程</h2><h3 id="1-生成新的hexo基础博客"><a href="#1-生成新的hexo基础博客" class="headerlink" title="1.生成新的hexo基础博客"></a>1.生成新的hexo基础博客</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">（<span class="number">1</span>）在git bath端输入</span><br><span class="line">hexo init <span class="comment">#初始化hexo博客</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s <span class="comment">#启动服务预览效果</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save <span class="comment">#安装hexo-deployer-git自动部署发布工具</span></span><br><span class="line">（<span class="number">2</span>）修改根目录里_config.yml</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#修改deploy项</span></span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https://github.com/TreeioView/TreeioView.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: main</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#修改站点sites信息</span></span><br><span class="line">title: TreeioView</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">description: <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">keywords: </span><br><span class="line">author: TreeioView</span><br><span class="line">language: en</span><br><span class="line">timezone: <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-配置新主题"><a href="#2-配置新主题" class="headerlink" title="2.配置新主题"></a>2.配置新主题</h3><p>根据主题相关文档</p><h3 id="3-上传博客"><a href="#3-上传博客" class="headerlink" title="3.上传博客"></a>3.上传博客</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g <span class="comment">#生成</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d<span class="comment">#本地文件上传到GitHub仓库</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="五、添加博客功能部件"><a href="#五、添加博客功能部件" class="headerlink" title="五、添加博客功能部件"></a>五、添加博客功能部件</h2><h3 id="1、添加看板娘"><a href="#1、添加看板娘" class="headerlink" title="1、添加看板娘"></a>1、添加看板娘</h3><h4 id="（1）下载配置文件"><a href="#（1）下载配置文件" class="headerlink" title="（1）下载配置文件"></a>（1）下载配置文件</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#在博客根目录/d/Blog/GitHubBlog的Git Bath端输入：</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-helper-live2d <span class="comment">#输入命令获取 live2d</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install live2d-widget-model-shizuku <span class="comment">#看板娘的模型下载</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="（2）看板娘模型地址"><a href="#（2）看板娘模型地址" class="headerlink" title="（2）看板娘模型地址"></a>（2）看板娘模型地址</h4><table><thead><tr><th>模型创作者</th><th>模型地址</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>xiazeyu</td><td><a href="https://github.com/xiazeyu/live2d-widget-models">xiazeyu&#x2F;live2d-widget-models：live2d-widget 的模型库.js (github.com)</a></td></tr><tr><td>ppet</td><td><a href="https://github.com/zenghongtu/live2d-model-assets">zenghongtu&#x2F;live2d-model-assets (github.com)</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/summerscar/live2dDemo">summerscar&#x2F;live2dDemo: live2dDemo http://summerscar.me/live2dDemo/</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/alg-wiki/AzurLaneL2DViewer">alg-wiki&#x2F;AzurLaneL2DViewer</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/Eikanya/Live2d-model">Eikanya&#x2F;Live2d-model: Live2d model collection</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/xiaoski/live2d_models_collection">xiaoski&#x2F;live2d_models_collection: Collections of live2d models</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/iCharlesZ/vscode-live2d-models">iCharlesZ&#x2F;vscode-live2d-models: VSCode看板娘模型库</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/luanshizhimei/live2d_models_collect">luanshizhimei&#x2F;live2d_models_collect: 个人收集的Live2D模型</a></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><a href="https://github.com/jianchengwang/live2d_models">jianchengwang&#x2F;live2d_models: 萌萌哒的看板娘</a></td></tr></tbody></table><h4 id="（3）xiazeyu模型介绍"><a href="#（3）xiazeyu模型介绍" class="headerlink" title="（3）xiazeyu模型介绍"></a>（3）xiazeyu模型介绍</h4><table><thead><tr><th>Liked：</th><th>Unliked：</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>model-z16 #白衣士女</td><td>model-tsumiki</td></tr><tr><td>model-wanko #碗中白犬</td><td>model-gf</td></tr><tr><td>model-unitychan #小双马尾</td><td>model-nietzsche #小长发卷</td></tr><tr><td>model-tororo #白猫</td><td>model-ni-j #小紫</td></tr><tr><td>model-shizuku #书桌女</td><td>model-nico #小狐狸</td></tr><tr><td>model-miku #初音未来</td><td>model-nito #小粉头</td></tr><tr><td>model-koharu #女海员</td><td>model-nipsilon #小粉双马尾</td></tr><tr><td>model-izumi #红衣女</td><td>model-chitose #西装男</td></tr><tr><td>model-hijiki #黑猫</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>model-hibiki #叉腰女</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>model-haruto #海员</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>model-epsilon2_1 #黄衣女</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>model-haru01 #短袖细双马尾</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>model-haru02 #校服细双马尾</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><h4 id="（4）在博客根目录-config-yml里添加代码"><a href="#（4）在博客根目录-config-yml里添加代码" class="headerlink" title="（4）在博客根目录_config.yml里添加代码"></a>（4）在博客根目录_config.yml里添加代码</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加卡通人物</span></span><br><span class="line">live2d:</span><br><span class="line">    enable: true</span><br><span class="line">    scriptFrom: local</span><br><span class="line">    model: </span><br><span class="line">        use: live2d-widget-model-shizuku </span><br><span class="line">    display: </span><br><span class="line">        position: left  <span class="comment">#模型位置</span></span><br><span class="line">        width: <span class="number">180</span>      <span class="comment">#模型宽度</span></span><br><span class="line">        height: <span class="number">390</span>     <span class="comment">#模型高度</span></span><br><span class="line">    mobile: </span><br><span class="line">        show: true      <span class="comment">#是否在手机端显示</span></span><br><span class="line">        scale: <span class="number">0.5</span></span><br><span class="line">    rect:</span><br><span class="line">        opacity: <span class="number">0.7</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="（5）强化版看板娘设置"><a href="#（5）强化版看板娘设置" class="headerlink" title="（5）强化版看板娘设置"></a>（5）强化版看板娘设置</h4><p><a href="https://baiziqing.github.io/2021/10/26/hexo-bo-ke-matery-zhu-ti-mei-hua-zhi-kan-ban-niang-neng-shuo-hua-neng-huan-zhuang-qie-huan-xiao-ren/">看板娘 | 白子卿 (baiziqing.github.io)</a></p><h3 id="2-添加音乐播放器"><a href="#2-添加音乐播放器" class="headerlink" title="2.添加音乐播放器"></a>2.添加音乐播放器</h3><h2 id="六、hexo相关技巧"><a href="#六、hexo相关技巧" class="headerlink" title="六、hexo相关技巧"></a>六、hexo相关技巧</h2><table><thead><tr><th>1.hexo相关</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>HTML中的注释是<!--注释内容--></td></tr><tr><td>在cmd端口打开Git Bath：start “Open Git Bash” “%SYSTEMDRIVE%\Program Files\Git\git-bash.exe”</td></tr><tr><td>GitHub和Gitee的博客都只能使用公有库；只有Coding的博客可以使用私有库。</td></tr><tr><td>hexo各插件功能：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/ioufev/articles/12119941.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/ioufev/articles/12119941.html</a></td></tr></tbody></table><table><thead><tr><th>2.npm命令</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>npm install hexo-server –save #更新server</td></tr><tr><td>npm ls –depth 0 #查看 npm 安装各 hexo 插件的情况</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
      
